    "template": "content",
    "texts": [
     "{\"template\":\"intro\",\"texts\":[\"There are a number of fare options available for older and disabled people.\"],\"link\":{\"image\":{}},\"image\":{},\"wrapped\":false}",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Freedom Passes\"}",
     "If you are over 60 or have a long-term disability and you live in London, you may be able to get a Freedom Pass. Find out how to apply on the \u003ca href=\"http://www.londoncouncils.gov.uk/services/freedompass/\"\u003eFreedom Pass website.\u003c/a\u003e ",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Other passes and discounts\"}",
     "For detailed information about fares and tickets, including concessionary travel and the Freedom Pass and 60+ London Oyster photocard, visit \u003ca href=\"/fares-and-payments/fares2018/index\"\u003efares\u003c/a\u003e .",
     "If you have an English National Concessionary Pass, this can be used on London's buses 24 hours a day.",
     "All wheelchair and mobility scooter users travel free on buses and trams. To find out if your scooter is suitable for travel, contact our \u003ca href=\"/transport-accessibility/learn-to-use-public-transport\"\u003etravel mentoring service\u003c/a\u003e .",
     "Companions and carers will have to pay for their travel.",
     "Our station staff will help you when using ticket machines, they will also answer any queries you may have about using your ticket or pass.",
     "{\"template\":\"htag\",\"level\":\"h3\",\"value\":\"Taxi and minicab fares\"}",
     "We set taxi (black cab) fares. The maximum fare payable for a taxi journey will be shown on the taximeter at the end of the journey.",
     " \u003ca href=\"/modes/taxis-and-minicabs/taxi-fares\"\u003eFind out more about typical fares for taxi passengers\u003c/a\u003e .",
     "Private hire (including minicab) fares are set by the private hire company but you should always ask for a quote when booking a private hire vehicle.",
     "Complaints about taxi or private hire fares and overcharging should be reported to us so we can investigate them. \u003ca href=\"/info-for/taxis-and-private-hire/contact-taxis-and-private-hire\"\u003eDetails of how to contact us are available here\u003c/a\u003e .",
     " \u003ca href=\"/cdn/static/cms/documents/assistance-dogs-know-your-rights.pdf\"\u003eFind out about your rights travelling by taxi, minicab or chauffeured vehicle with an assistance dog\u003c/a\u003e ."
    ],
